          "recommendationid": "218113140",
          "refunded": false,
          "review": "This was my main game, but it has serious issues because the anti-cheat system doesn’t seem to work properly. The game often feels overrun by cheaters, and there’s usually nothing you can do except forfeit.\r\n\r\nI’d like to play more and continue supporting the game, but nowadays it only feels enjoyable if you play with a full 5-stack and use a third-party competitive platform like FACEIT.\r\n\r\nI’ve also tried several things to improve my Trust Factor. I’m an experienced player, but it feels like no matter what you do, you end up with low Trust Factor — play well and you get reported, new players get low Trust Factor, and actual cheaters do too. It doesn’t seem like the developers are taking proper care of players who genuinely want to play fairly and maintain a good environment. I’ve already tried everything people recommend to improve Trust Factor, including reading discussions, guides, and watching YouTube videos, but nothing has worked.",
