          "review": "After 1234.5 hours of playtime, I would rate this game 6 7 out of 10.\n\nJust a little bit more things that will make this a better game:\n- Good anti-cheat\n- 128-tick (Yes, subtick didn't work)\n- Better hit registration / netcode\n- Consistent movement & spray behavior\n- Less peekers advantage\n- Ban waves that actually scare cheaters\n- MM ranks that actually mean something\n- Better solo-queue experience\n- Less rank decay nonsense\n- Less stuttering / frame drops\n- Fewer random packet loss issues\n- More global server coverage\n- Better map rotation\n- More operation?\n- Less stale active duty pool\n- Better demo system\n- More useful practice tools\n- Cleaner inventory UI\n- Less buggy skin finishes\n- More transparency with drops\n- No random skin breakage after updates\n- Actual communication from Valve\n- Roadmaps\n- Listening to long-term players",
